ng money in lieu of an offer letter for a job opportunity in NeST you are encouraged to bring such matters to our attention by reporting it at <strong><a href=\"mailto:contact@nestgroup.net\">contact@nestgroup.net<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Recruitment Fraud The NeST Group is a purely merit-based employer, who provides equal opportunity to competent professionals irrespective of biases. NeST neither charges any fee, nor require any money deposits from jobseekers at any stage of recruitment nor collect any fees from educational institutions for participation in a recruitment event. NeST also do not send [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"blocksy_meta":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3561"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3561"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3561\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":6781,"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3561\/revisions\/6781"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/nestdigital.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3561"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}